Metcash Trading Africa Agrees to Sell Franchise Unit to Shoprite Checkers

-- B y   N a s r e e n   S e r i a
-- 
2011-03-08T13:34:35Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-08/metcash-trading-africa-agrees-to-sell-franchise-unit-to-shoprite-checkers.html
Metcash Trading Africa Ltd. said it
agreed to sell its franchise unit, which includes Friendly and
Seven Eleven supermarket brands, to  Shoprite Holdings Ltd. (SHP)   The sale is subject to approval by  South Africa ’s antitrust
regulator, Johannesburg-based Metcash said in an e-mailed
statement today, without disclosing the purchase price. The
franchise unit will be integrated into Shoprite’s OK division,
Metcash said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nasreen Seria at 
 nseria@bloomberg.net  